  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2426840/extras/7edd711b85e49447cf2f3bf811e8d6da.poster.avif?t=1769818627\" width=588 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2426840/extras/7edd711b85e49447cf2f3bf811e8d6da.webm?t=1769818627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>is a fast paced, top down, dungeon crawling action-rpg with roguelike elements in which every death is a lesson on how to move forward. Progress through six  distinct areas, collecting game changing items, leveling up and learning how to best fight each enemy you encounter along the way. Mix item effects together for game-breaking combinations or force your way through on your skill alone, all the while being hunted by one of the four unique dragons that mysteriously pursue the player.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2426840/extras/2044d1df01a608150cf69d0aa97424d7.poster.avif?t=1769818627\" width=630 height=460 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2426840/extras/2044d1df01a608150cf69d0aa97424d7.webm?t=1769818627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2426840/extras/2044d1df01a608150cf69d0aa97424d7.mp4?t=1769818627\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Move as fast as you can move your mouse to dodge, slash and shoot your way through over 200 hand-made arenas. Battle rats, spiders, ents, fire elementals, living skeletons and more.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2426840/extras/57eaa8a5e45ec641c80421055752618f.avif?t=1769818627\" width=600 height=120 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>4 playable characters, each with their own unique abilities and stat progressions<br><br></li><li>73 different items, most adding completely new ways to play<br><br></li><li>33 enemy types, each with their own behaviors and abilities<br><br></li><li>6 challenging boss battles <br><br></li><li>Over 200 handcrafted rooms to fight through<br><br></li><li>Player Achievements, World Encyclopedia, Secrets and more!!!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2426840/extras/ead97592479ce72b2379e8d457d7ca94.avif?t=1769818627\" width=600 height=120 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2426840/extras/7edd711b85e49447cf2f3bf811e8d6da.poster.avif?t=1769818627\" width=588 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2426840/extras/7edd711b85e49447cf2f3bf811e8d6da.webm?t=1769818627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>is a fast paced, top down, dungeon crawling action-rpg with roguelike elements in which every death is a lesson on how to move forward. Progress through six  distinct areas, collecting game changing items, leveling up and learning how to best fight each enemy you encounter along the way. Mix item effects together for game-breaking combinations or force your way through on your skill alone, all the while being hunted by one of the four unique dragons that mysteriously pursue the player.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2426840/extras/2044d1df01a608150cf69d0aa97424d7.poster.avif?t=1769818627\" width=630 height=460 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2426840/extras/2044d1df01a608150cf69d0aa97424d7.webm?t=1769818627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2426840/extras/2044d1df01a608150cf69d0aa97424d7.mp4?t=1769818627\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Move as fast as you can move your mouse to dodge, slash and shoot your way through over 200 hand-made arenas. Battle rats, spiders, ents, fire elementals, living skeletons and more.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2426840/extras/57eaa8a5e45ec641c80421055752618f.avif?t=1769818627\" width=600 height=120 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>4 playable characters, each with their own unique abilities and stat progressions<br><br></li><li>73 different items, most adding completely new ways to play<br><br></li><li>33 enemy types, each with their own behaviors and abilities<br><br></li><li>6 challenging boss battles <br><br></li><li>Over 200 handcrafted rooms to fight through<br><br></li><li>Player Achievements, World Encyclopedia, Secrets and more!!!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2426840/extras/ead97592479ce72b2379e8d457d7ca94.avif?t=1769818627\" width=600 height=120 /></span>",
